Install (just one step):

    python2 setup.py install --prefix=/usr

To start ncmpy, run:

    ncmpy

Main configuration file is /etc/ncmpy.conf
Configuration sample is /usr/share/ncmpy/ncmpy.conf.example
Edit and copy it to /etc/ncmpy.conf
And you can also create a user-scope configuration file ~/.ncmpy/ncmpy.conf

Default lyrics directory is ~/.ncmpy/lyrics

Enjoy!
